{
  "texts": [
    "Exploration of other neuron models, with unique features complementing SFA, is needed.",
    "Additionally, higher-order spike response models (SRMs) could provide enhanced dynamics that may augment learning but require profound investigation.",
    "The search for learning rules aligned with SFAs complexities remains a challenge, necessitating innovative algorithms to optimize adaptive neuron functionality.",
    "In the future, research in SFA-based neuron models could focus on how the different implementation options for SFA (intrinsic changes of the spiking threshold vs. inhibitory input vs. short-term synaptic plasticity), including their different time-scales, affect the coding properties of a network.",
    "Hence, investigate if some motifs are more suitable for certain computations than others."
  ]
}